{
  "stem": "2996.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the way I built an audience, that I had higher rating for the station than any of the so-called network stations.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The local stuff [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So one of them was The Atomic Age is Here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was preaching how to-- how to understand what is happening on-- on the international scene.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Atomic Age is Here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know who Leo Szilard was?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Leo Szilard who took Einstein to Roosevelt to explain-- I interviewed Leo Szilard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wrote the whole interview and I had a guy with a good voice, without a German accent, do all of the shows.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of them didn't know Joe Roos existed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Leo Szilard talked me into doing a show once a week, The Atomic Age is Here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got to tell you a funny one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a fellow in Pasadena who was an [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This guy called and said, what do I know about the atomics?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he put me together with a man who-- whose name I can't remember-- was an expert at it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was always a very well-known professor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He helped me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He got me ones who-- I shouldn't say I did-- I arranged the interview with the fellow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he came there at the right time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I interviewed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I wrote out the series of questions, for a-- a guy who really was no more than an announcer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when he was finished-- well, he was driven there, I should say-- when he was finished, I took him to his car.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said goodbye to him, while thanking him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The driver left the key inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Here's a guy who could blow up the whole world.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you should have seen what problems they had to get back into the car.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
